results.name: Denominators of exponential expansion of (3/(2*log(1+x)))*(1 - 1/(1+x)^(2/3)).
comment: For the numerators see A284862, also for details.
The z-sequence for the Sheffer triangle A225466 is 2*A284862(n)/a(n).
formula: a(n) = denominator(r(n)), with the rationals (in lowest terms) r(n) = [x^n/n!] (1/log((1+x)^(1/3)))*(1 - 1/(1+x)^(2/3)).
results.author: _Wolfdieter Lang_, Apr 09 2017
